# An-AI-chatbot
A custom-built AI chatbot

## Description

An-AI-Chatbot is an experimental project aiming to create a human-like interaction experience.

## How to use

Enter your message in the input field.

Press Enter to send the message.

After long chatting, you may need to refresh the page, so click on the Clear chat button.

## Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/PerenNana/An-AI-chatbot.git
cd An-AI-chatbot
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

## Usage
Start the chatbot by running the frontend:
```bash
cd chatbot

streamlit run app.py
```
Launching the backend:
```bash
uvicorn backend:app --reload
```
Starting Ollama:
```bash
ollama run llama3
```

